author: gtully
msg: resolve https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/AMQ-2473 - issue with jmstemplate were producers are closed before transaction commits which is fine save when failover ocurrs. the producers need to be replayed to allow tracked messages to be replayed. added the capability to track and relay transaction producers. Can be disabled if producers out live transactions
